These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, banana, cauliflower, watermelon
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the far left##1
2. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
3. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | pumpkin | banana | cauliflower | watermelon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite, hot-chocolate, lemonade
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | mirinda | lemonade | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, collecting, chess, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | sudoku | chess | collecting | filmmaking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, drama, western, sports
1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | martial-arts | sports | western |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
