2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | soccer | water-polo | lacrosse | tennis |

