.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, spinach, banana, peach
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating spinach is between the person eating plum and the person eating peach##2
3. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
4. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | peach | spinach | plum | banana |

