.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, ambient, electronic, soul
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient | salsa | soul |

 